; HotCRP offline-review marker lines.
;
; `==*==` and `==-==` are template/control lines. They are highlighted
; strongly to discourage edits. Zed extensions do not currently expose an API
; for making arbitrary line ranges read-only.

(template_line) @keyword
(field_marker) @tag
(separator_line) @punctuation.delimiter
(comment_line) @comment
(paper_line) @title
(score_option) @constant
(field_name) @property
